# Dev: `.env.development` uses `/api/v1` (Vite proxy → localhost:8005).
#
# Vercel + API on Render: set in Vercel → Environment (Production + Preview):
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api/v1
#   BACKEND_ORIGIN=https://your-api.onrender.com
# (BACKEND_ORIGIN is read by api/v1/[...slug].js serverless proxy; no /api/v1 suffix.)
#
# Or call the API directly (set CORS + FRONTEND_ORIGIN on the server):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com/api/v1
